					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Capcom's solution as seen in <em>Mega Man</em>: Draw only the player character layered, and draw the player character frontmost.
<br />
<br />Konami's solution as seen in <em>Contra</em>: Instead of drawing layers, draw a top half and a bottom half. Also seen in the HKO <em>Kart Fighter</em> and the pirate <em>Super Mario World</em>. May be seen in other games where the artists have also worked on the MSX.</div>

